name: Head Pot
description: I call this creature a Head Pot. Head Pots, not to be mistaken with Pot Heads will come up out of the ground only for a moment’s notice when no-one is around, and then go back into the Earth. Unlike Pot Heads, Head Pots like to stay really low. Don’t stare in their eyes for too long, or you can become a Head Pot too. Twitter (@crypto_wook)
